summary: after more than a year of feeling horrible and worthless, i finally went to the doctor this week to start on some medication,...
body: after more than a year of feeling horrible and worthless, i finally went to the doctor this week to start on some medication, and just now i scheduled myself for a therapy appointment. i’m feeling the worst i ever have in my entire life, but at least i’m proud of myself in this moment. i have hope. thank you @danielhowell for showing me it’s not weak to ask for help. thank you for showing me it’s brave and courageous to want to get better. thank you for everything.
